            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <salute>Dear Sir,—</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am obliged to you for your note. The subject of Right-handedness is a very curious one, but I have never attended to it, and can give you no additional facts.<ref target="#foot.f1"/></p>
<p>Ch. Darwin. <lb resp="#mjhawkins"/> <lb resp="#mjhawkins"/></p>
<p rend="left">20th Feb. 1868.</p> 
